A program that allows a business client to create project feature requests.

Current project status:
DB definition and initial front-end layout prototype.

To run the app locally:
1. Clone the repo
2. cd to the top-level feature_requester directory
[Optional: python3 -m venv some_venv
           . some_venv/bin/activate]
3. pip install -e .
4. export FLASK_APP=feature_requester
  [In Windows: set FLASK_APP=feature_requester]
5. flask initdb (if this is your first time)
6. cd feature_requester
7. bower install
8. flask run
9: go to localhost:5000 in the browser
